=head1 DESCRIPTION

Writes the MIME content of the email to an S3 bucket.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ActionFailurePolicy => Str

A policy that states what to do in the case of failure. The action will
fail if there are configuration errors. For example, the specified the
bucket has been deleted.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RoleArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM Role to use while writing to
S3. This role must have access to the s3:PutObject, kms:Encrypt, and
kms:GenerateDataKey APIs for the given bucket.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> S3Bucket => Str

The bucket name of the S3 bucket to write to.


=head2 S3Prefix => Str

The S3 prefix to use for the write to the s3 bucket.


=head2 S3SseKmsKeyId => Str

The KMS Key ID to use to encrypt the message in S3.



